item.title: Do You Know the Answer? Find Out How to Spell 'Urinal' Here!
item.description: Introduction Do you know how to spell ‘urinal’? If you’re like many people, you may not know the answer. But don’t worry! In this blog post, we’ll explain how to spell ‘urinal’ and provide you with the steps you need to take to spell it correctly. Definition of Urinal A urinal is a plumbing fixture that is used by men to urinate. It is usually found in public restrooms and is designed to be used while standing up.
